#: includes/admin/class-integrations.php
msgid ""
"Connect your Form leads to FluentCRM and instantly add new contacts when a "
"form is submitted. Perfect for automated email campaigns and segmented "
"marketing."
msgstr ""
"Verbind uw formulierleads met FluentCRM en voeg direct nieuwe contacten toe "
"wanneer een formulier wordt ingediend. Perfect voor geautomatiseerde "
"e-mailcampagnes en gesegmenteerde marketing."

#: includes/admin/class-integrations.php
msgid ""
"Create Mailchimp newsletter signups directly from your form submissions. "
"Automatically grow your audience and engage your subscribers."
msgstr ""
"Creëer Mailchimp-nieuwsbriefaanmeldingen rechtstreeks vanuit uw "
"formulierinzendingen. Laat uw publiek automatisch groeien en betrek uw "
"abonnees."

#: includes/admin/class-integrations.php
msgid ""
"Sync form submissions directly to Google Sheets in real time. Perfect for "
"reporting, analytics, or team collaboration without manual data entry."
msgstr ""
"Synchroniseer formulierinzendingen rechtstreeks en in realtime met Google "
"Spreadsheets. Perfect voor rapportage, analyse of teamsamenwerking zonder "
"handmatige gegevensinvoer."

#: includes/admin/class-integrations.php
msgid ""
"Add subscribers to your MailPoet mailing lists as soon as they submit a "
"form. Automate your newsletter growth and keep your audience engaged."
msgstr ""
"Voeg abonnees toe aan uw MailPoet-mailinglijsten zodra ze een formulier "
"indienen. Automatiseer de groei van uw nieuwsbrief en houd uw publiek "
"betrokken."

